{"tid":444211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣「禁掛五星旗」提案通過  政府兩月內須回應","createTime":"2017-10-22T10:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T13:30:24.000Z","uid":35790,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"30da6830611fe33cc4a27c2fd59416d431bd46e2","tid":444211,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"台灣「禁掛五星旗」提案通過政府兩月內須回應<br />\n<br />\n2017/10/22 17:13&nbsp;14590<br />\n<br />\n之前才有網友為了與中國不同時區，而提案更改台灣時區，又有網友在《公共政策網路參與平臺》提案要求台灣應該禁掛中國五星旗，連署附議人數與今天通過，相關機關須於今年12月22日前回應。<br />\n<br />\n提案人表示，台灣與中國一直是敵對關係，中國不但不承認台灣是主權獨立國家，也不放棄分化、分裂台灣，但台灣對於中國的文攻武嚇卻沒有太多作為，中國五星旗更是在台灣各個地方出現，台灣人民變得沒有危機意識，因此「提議增設型法條文分裂國土外患內亂罪，禁止中國五星旗在台灣公開懸掛、展示、陳列出現。」<br />\n（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171022/1227050/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20171022%2F1227050%2F&d=uNgeisI3UP3VmGMXQXy0T8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a35f99a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171022/1227050/</a>"},{"pid":"754f367e6e1cb0fbf4743d946a062942e22ec4ea","tid":444211,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b3d71f34543b11f1e8c0c68a11b783a12a7e8f","tid":444211,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"公共政策網路参與平臺 <br />\n<a href=\"https://join.gov.tw/idea/detail/dcdc494d-f8af-4714-af83-ad9affc2c67f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjoin.gov.tw%2Fidea%2Fdetail%2Fdcdc494d-f8af-4714-af83-ad9affc2c67f&d=uNgeisI3UP3VmGMXQXy0T8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6f741438\" target=\"_blank\">https://join.gov.tw/idea/detail/dcdc494d-f8af-4714-af83-ad9affc2c67f</a>"},{"pid":"f4ca01ccf17610a0f3f51d0550cfa41647b3f96e","tid":444211,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl